name: SynthPudding
description:
SynthPudding is a model excels in generating compelling sci-fi narratives with a particular focus on female characters. SynthPudding is especially well-suited for generating content related to mechamusume, mecha, cyberpunk, android, cyborg and futuristic themes. but also can do a variety of genres such as fantasy.

the girls from this model might be genetically engineered.

Available steps: 20
Recommend steps: 30+

Resolution:
image compose change by resolution
512x768 (recommended)
768x1152 or above (recommended for more details)
For landscape images, reverse the width and height values accordingly.

Hires step: 10-30
Hires.fix: R-ESRGAN 4x+Anime6b
Denoising strength: 0.4

VAE: Baked (vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned)

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

If there's anything you need, please don't hesitate to let me know.

**Please note that you are solely responsible for any images created using this model.
